---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy - Side Badger"
  description="Our cookie policy is simple: we don't use them for tracking. We're not interested in your data. We're just here to help you split bills, not to follow you around the internet. It's the cookie policy you've always dreamed of."
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-header fade-up">
        <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content glass fade-up">
        <div class="placeholder-notice">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <circle cx="8" cy="9" r="1"/>
            <circle cx="15" cy="9" r="1"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="14" r="1"/>
            <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="1"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="11" r="1"/>
          </svg>
          <h2>Cookie Policy Coming Soon</h2>
          <p>The actual cookie policy content will be loaded from the Side Badger API.</p>
          <p class="text-muted">Spoiler alert: We don't really use cookies for tracking.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="quick-summary">
          <h3>The Cookie Situation (It's Pretty Boring)</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>No tracking cookies.</strong> We're not following you around the internet. That's creepy.</li>
            <li><strong>No advertising cookies.</strong> We don't show ads, so we don't need to profile you.</li>
            <li><strong>No analytics cookies.</strong> We're not counting your visits or measuring your engagement.</li>
            <li><strong>Functional cookies only.</strong> Just the basics to make the app work (like keeping you logged in).</li>
            <li><strong>No cookie consent popup.</strong> Because we don't need one. You're welcome.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="cookie-illustration">
          <p>üç™ ‚Üí ü¶° ‚Üí üö´</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Badger sees cookie. Badger says no thanks.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="api-placeholder">
          <code>// Cookie policy content will be fetched from:</code>
          <code>// GET app.sidebadger.com/api/legal/cookies</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    min-height: 70vh;
  }

  .legal-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .legal-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .placeholder-notice {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .placeholder-notice svg {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .placeholder-notice h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .placeholder-notice p {
    max-width: none;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .quick-summary {
    background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .quick-summary h3 {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .quick-summary ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .quick-summary li {
    padding: var(--space-sm) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    position: relative;
  }

  .quick-summary li::before {
    content: 'üö´';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }

  .cookie-illustration {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .cookie-illustration p:first-child {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .api-placeholder {
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .api-placeholder code {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }
</style>
